Requirement document: Lists the things to be taken into consideration while
disigning are architecturing sme_async.

1) Loosely coupled architecture i.e various components must be self sufficients
   and not dependent on other components

2) Network I/O, File I/O must be plugable and customizable.

3) File I/O must supports various ways of doing async i.e callback, thread
   poll, libaio like.

4) Must support for signal and timer events

5) No locks

6) Must support custom events
